docs.title: Commands
docs.text:
• mkdocs new [dir-name] - Create a new project.
  • mkdocs serve - Start the live-reloading docs server.
  • mkdocs build - Build the documentation site.
  • mkdocs -h - Print help message and exit.

docs.title: Project layout
docs.text:
mkdocs.yml    # The configuration file.
docs/
    index.md  # The documentation homepage.
    metadata-architecture.md
    ...       # Other markdown pages, images and other files.

docs.title: Metadata Architecture
docs.text:
flowchart TB
  subgraph Inputs[Data Inputs]
      direction TB
      NRM
      PostgreSQL
      Other[Other<br>WebApp, Healthy Forest Restoration]     
  end

  subgraph Review
    direction TB
    Spreadsheet --> Application --> PowerPoint
  end

  NRM --> Spreadsheet
  PostgreSQL --> Spreadsheet
  Other --> Spreadsheet

  subgraph EDW
    direction TB
    Approve{Approve?}
    subgraph EDWIngest[EDW Ingest]
      FME
      edw[(EDW)]
    end

    FME --> edw
  end

  PowerPoint --> Approve
  Approve --> |Yes| FME
  Approve --> |No| Inputs
